<br>
Not pissed at the cleric who won, she was just doing what the group leader said to do, to roll.  But I'm kinda pissed that Cameljon took an item that would obviously benefit the warrior (who's still mostly in crafted or worse at lvl 51) and randomed it out to the entire group.<br>
<br>
